# Cursor Rules for js2pi-part-1 Project

## Language Requirements

- **ALL conversations and communications must be conducted in English only**

## Project Context

This is a deep dive learning project following Andrej Karpathy's ["Neural Networks: Zero to Hero"](https://karpathy.ai/zero-to-hero.html) course, building neural networks from scratch including micrograd, makemore, MLPs, WaveNet, and GPT.

## Code Style Guidelines

- Follow Python PEP 8 style guidelines
- Use clear, descriptive variable and function names
- Write comprehensive comments for complex neural network concepts
- Use meaningful docstrings for functions and classes

## Project Goals

- Gain experience in neural networks and understand how they work
- Gain experience using uv package manager
- Develop ability to use Python, uv and Jupyter notebooks
- Build understanding from backpropagation to modern transformers
